message:
Task complete.

What I delivered and verified:
- /workspace/solution.py — final solution (reads N from stdin, prints count of integers ≤ N with exactly 9 divisors). Verified on samples (N=200 -> 3, N=4e12 -> 407073) and with exhaustive checks up to 5000.
- /workspace/eval_test.py — test harness used for brute-force verification on small N.
- /workspace/evaluation.txt — evaluation scores and reasoning.

How to run:
- Example: echo 200 | python3 /workspace/solution.py
- Or: python3 /workspace/solution.py < input.txt

No further action required.
